#: src-ru/data/events_slug.xml.rawclobber:1252
msgid ""
"data/events_slug.xml.rawclobber$//eventList[@name=\"SLUG_DRINK_ROCK\"]/event[2]/text"
msgstr ""
"岩石族能够检测出饮料中含有大量强效镇静剂，这让他感到有些昏昏欲睡（岩石族的消"
